sentences.en: A problem occurred when the wizard attempted to rename a registry key.
sentences.cn: 向导试图重命名注册表项时发生错误.

sentences.en: Can't rename the Inbox , Outbox, Sent Items , or Deleted Items folder.
sentences.cn: 不能重命名以下文件夹:收件箱, 发件箱, 已发送的邮件,已删除的邮件.

sentences.en: Cannot rename a sheet with the same name as another sheet.
sentences.cn: 已有同名工作表存在,不能以此名称设置此工作表.

sentences.en: Could not rename links in |; the file is currently in use.
sentences.cn: 无法重命名|中的链接; 此文件正在使用.

sentences.en: For more information, see How to: Rename an Identifier.
sentences.cn: 有关更多信息, 请参见如何: 重命名标识符.

sentences.en: In order to have resounding name, she plans to rename herself.
sentences.cn: 为了使名字更响亮, 她打算改名.

sentences.en: Redeploy a new instance of the list and rename'% 1'to'% 2 '.
sentences.cn: 重新部署列表的新实例,并将“%1 ” 重命名为 “ %2 ”.

sentences.en: Right - click a playlist of tracks you can add, remove or rename tracks.
sentences.cn: 右键单击播放列表中的曲目可添加, 清除或重命名曲目.

sentences.en: Sitemap Pane: Add, remove, rename, and organize the pages in your design.
sentences.cn: 站点地图面板: 在设计中增加 、 删除 、 重命名以及组织页面.

sentences.en: Tel Aviv's Kings Square was renamed Yitzhak Rabin Square.
sentences.cn: 特拉维夫的国王广场更名为伊扎克·拉宾广场。

sentences.en: The Registry Editor cannot rename % 1. Error while renaming value.
sentences.cn: 注册表编辑器无法重命名%1. 重命名值时出现错误.

sentences.en: To avoid confusion between the two methods, you can rename your method.
sentences.cn: 为了避免这两个方法之间发生混淆, 可以重命名您的方法.

sentences.en: Unable to rename macro A macro with that name already exists.
sentences.cn: 要为巨集重新命名的名称,已有其他巨集使用.

sentences.en: Unable to rename temporary table on server to'| '.
sentences.cn: 无法将服务器上的临时表重命名为 “ |”.

sentences.en: You may rename all the items as you wish.
sentences.cn: 你可以把所有项目的名字修改成你想要的名字.

trans.tran_en: to give something a new name
